      'README.md': `# React + TypeScript Template

A modern React application with TypeScript and Vite.

## Getting Started

1. Install dependencies:
\`\`\`bash
npm install
\`\`\`

2. Start development server:
\`\`\`bash
npm run dev
\`\`\`

3. Build for production:
\`\`\`bash
npm run build
\`\`\`

## Features

- ‚ö° Vite for fast development
- ‚öõÔ∏è React 18 with TypeScript
- üéØ Hot Module Replacement (HMR)
- üìè ESLint for code linting
- üé® Modern CSS with CSS modules support

## Project Structure

\`\`\`
src/
  ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ assets/        # Static assets
  ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ App.tsx        # Main App component
  ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ App.css        # App styles
  ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ main.tsx       # Entry point
  ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ index.css      # Global styles
\`\`\`
`
